data.title: Jennifer Montague on LinkedIn: Excited for this conversation next month!
data.meta_description: Excited for this conversation next month!
data.text: WOMEN IN UTILITIES! How can you prepare yourself to ADVANCE your career? Learn from Leaders! Meet NiSource's Jennifer Montague, President of Columbia Gas of Virginia at The ADVANCE Woman Leadership Program for Utilities. Jennifer will share her journey with you, where it led her, and what prompted her to focus on her own career leadership! Prepare to be inspired! This immersive Leadership Program is in Downtown Chicago. You will meet other women eager to ADVANCE their careers in the energy industry and leave with a plan, playbook, and concrete next steps here: https://lnkd.in/ezJQd8Ej
